member.example:
This sample shows how to call GetIntAsync with required parameters and parse the result.

var client = new ValueTypesClient().GetIntClient(<1.0.0>);

Response response = await client.GetIntAsync();

JsonElement result = JsonDocument.Parse(response.ContentStream).RootElement;
Console.WriteLine(result.GetProperty("property").ToString());

member.remarks:
Below is the JSON schema for the response payload.

Response Body:

Schema for IntProperty:
{
  property: number, # Required. Property
}

